    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "1. Human in the Loop (HITL)\nWhat is Human in the Loop?\n\nHuman in the Loop means:\n\nAI or automation performs most of the work, but a human approves, reviews, or modifies something before the workflow continues.\n\nInstead of:\n\nAI → Send Email\n\nWe do:\n\nAI → Human Approval → Send Email\nWhy do we need it?\n\nAI can make mistakes.\n\nExamples:\n\nSending offer letters\nProcessing refunds\nApproving leave requests\nSending legal documents\n\nA human should verify before final action.",
